<tr><td bgcolor="#363636">
<a name="aegis_of_life"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Aegis of Life - AC 12</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/shields_and_held_items.shtml">Shields and Held Items</a><BR>
Weight: 9.5 - BAR, DEF, DWF, ERU, GNM, HEF, HLF, HIE, HUM, ELF<BR>
Classes: <a href="/cleric/armour/shields_and_held_items.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/paladin/armour/shields_and_held_items.shtml">PAL</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/superior_healing.shtml?spellID=654">Superior Healing</a><BR>
Charges: 1<BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(WIS +10) (Sv Disease +25) </font>
<BR>
Obtained through the <a href="/quests/aegis_of_life.shtml?questID=149">Aegis of Life</a> quest<BR>
Can also be worn in the back slot.<BR>
Submitted By: Naare E'tienee<BR>

