<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Khalim Richelieu</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-07 06:45:36</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>  Actually, there is a spot with 3 standing putrid skels (The only ones that will stand up in the entire camp)  These are the placeholders, I believe one is for the live version, one for the dead version, and the third is a static.  I've now killed live grimrot 8 times, and dead grimrot 3 times, doing nothing to make him spawn besides killing the standing putrids under the little hut, where he himself spawns.</font></td></tr></table>
